pageProduct.name: SUP Shots ZZZ Sleep 8x50ml Vials
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Lemon Balm, Passionfruit Seed Extract and Chamomile to make your dreams come true.

INVEST IN REST
Work hard. Play hard. Sleep hard. We are in the middle of a sleep revolution and if you aren't already on board, get ready. There is compelling evidence revealing the power of sleep for just about every human function. However, with our busy, modern lifestyles, it's hard to find enough time to recharge.

WHY SHOT SUP?
Drink your supplements on-the-go with our super shots. This formulation is raising the bar for sleep. SUP's herbs and botanicals have been traditionally consumed to help: 
  • Relax your body, mind and soul
  • Benefit sleep
  • Foster a peaceful mind
  • Bring some ying to your yang
SHOTSUP

Size: 8x50mL

KEY FEATURES

• Relax your body, mind and soul
• Benefit sleep
• Foster a peaceful mind
• Bring some ying to your yang
• Shot your vitamins on-the-go

Warnings

Shake before opening. Do not use if tamper evident seal is broken or missing. Store below 25?°C.

Ingredients

Water, Apple juice concentrate, Stabiliser (trehalose), Natural apple flavour, Natural peach flavour, Banana extract, L-Tryptophan, Ziziphi spinosae seed extract, Stabiliser (HM pectin), Brown rice ferment, Lemon balm, Flavour (citric acid monohydrate) xseed extract, Chamomile extract, Sweetener (steviol glycoside), Bitter melon extract.

Allergen Free From: Dairy| Egg| Gluten| Peanuts

Directions

SHOT 1 SUP (50mL) before you hit the hay.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25oC
